objenome.op

Class Variable<X>

  • java.lang.Object
    • objenome.op.Variable<X>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DoubleVariable, Variable.ObjectVariable

    public abstract class Variable<X>
extends java.lang.Object
    Instances of Variable are named values for use in a program tree. Variables are not nodes, so they must be wrapped in a VariableNode to be used in a program. The data-type of a variable is determined at construction and must not then be changed.
    Since:
    2.0
    See Also:
    VariableNode
